# Eleventy Build Requirement

This project uses Eleventy (11ty) as a static site generator. Source files (`.html`, `_includes/*.njk`) are templates — the browser-ready output lives in `_site/`.

**After every change, no matter how minor, run:**

```bash
npm run build
```

This applies to changes to any `.html` page, any `_includes/*.njk` partial, `.eleventy.js`, or `_data/` files. Do not skip the build step even for single-line edits.

CSS (`css/`) and JS (`js/`) files are passthrough-copied and do not require a rebuild, but running `npm run build` after those changes is still fine.
